    </h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200">
      <li>â€¢ <strong>Conservative:</strong> Best for debt payoff and building emergency funds</li>
      <li>â€¢ <strong>Balanced:</strong> Good mix of security and growth for most people</li>
      <li>â€¢ <strong>Aggressive:</strong> Maximize wealth building if you have high income stability</li>
      <li>â€¢ You can always adjust your budget as your situation changes</li>
      <li>â€¢ The AI will learn from your spending patterns and improve recommendations over time</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
